thread.title_full: Everyone Loves Buttons Inc.® reviewed by LJAL

author: LJAL
title: LJAL
text: Was very happy with the quality and fast turn around of my order. Customer service was great too. My only critique would be to see what I am creating there on the screen. I can do this for rubber stamps that I ordered from an online company., for example. Otherwise 4.5 stars!
